description: Mixed redevelopment comprising fifty-six 1-bedroomed flats, eight 1-bedroomed studio flats, thirty-four 2-bedroomed and six 3 bedroomed self contained flats together with 1200 square metres of B1 office floor space in one nine storey and one twelve storey building together with basement car and cycle parking, plant, refuse and amenity facilities and alterations to access.
